</span><span> </span><span>江西省南昌市昌北二小</span></span><br />\n<span><span>74</span><span> </span><span>我心目中的“真”教师</span><span> </span><span>杨文风</span><span> </span><span>湖北省黄冈市黄梅县八角亭中学</span></span><br />\n<span><span>75</span><span> </span><span>雪育春心</span><span> </span><span>德庆尼玛</span><span> </span><span>西藏自治区拉萨中学</span></span><br />\n<span><span>76</span><span> </span><span>谢谢你那些年给我的温暖——致我的老师</span><span> </span><span>梁采仪（学生）</span><span> </span><span>广东省云浮市新兴县一中高一12班</span></span><br />\n<span><span>77</span><span> </span><span>世界上最小的台阶</span><span> </span><span>冯根林</span><span> </span><span>安徽省滁州市全椒县教育局</span></span><br />\n<span><span>78</span><span> </span><span>我爱王老师</span><span> </span><span>蔡晓静（学生）</span><span> </span><span>\"福建省蒲田市涵江区江口育才小学</span></span><br />\n<span>六年二班\"</span><br />\n<span><span>79</span><span> </span><span>毕业笑着说再见</span><span> </span><span>曾飞英</span><span> </span><span>广东省珠海市香洲区前山小学</span></span><br />\n<span><span>80</span><span> </span><span>教师的幸福是学生给的</span><span> </span><span>马 &nbsp;娜</span><span> </span><span>陕西省渭南市大荔县城关镇云棋小学</span></span><br />\n<span><span>81</span><span> </span><span>心路</span><span> </span><span>李雨姝</span><span> </span><span>广东省珠海市香洲区第五小学</span></span><br />\n<span><span>82</span><span> </span><span>\"淡然与温暖交织的爱</span></span><br />\n<span><span>——我的老师叶飞霞\"</span><span> </span><span>温圆玲（学生）</span><span> </span><span>福建农林大学马克思主义学院</span></span><br />\n<span><span>83</span><span> </span><span>陌上花开</span><span> </span><span>暮 &nbsp;岚</span><span> </span><span>安徽省六安市城北小学</span></span><br />\n<span><span>84</span><span> </span><span>我的大学老师老林</span><span> </span><span>方淑婷（学生）</span><span> </span><span>山东财经大学法学院法学四班</span></span><br />\n<span><span>85</span><span> </span><span>为师十年</span><span> </span><span>安丽萍</span><span> </span><span>\"内蒙古自治区呼伦贝尔市牙克石市</span></span><br />\n<span>第一中学\"</span><br />\n<span><span>86</span><span> </span><span>眺望理想信念的远方</span><span> </span><span>叶显发</span><span> </span><span>湖北大学教育学院教授</