s/userup/1003/1R0525Q4W_lit.jpg\" width=\"280\" border=\"0\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.zgxymyw.cn/uploads/userup/1003/1R053433017.jpg\" target=\"_blank\"><img height=\"220\" alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.zgxymyw.cn/uploads/userup/1003/1R053433017_lit.jpg\" width=\"163\" border=\"0\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.zgxymyw.cn/uploads/userup/1003/1R055463396.jpg\" target=\"_blank\"><img height=\"186\" alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.zgxymyw.cn/uploads/userup/1003/1R055463396_lit.jpg\" width=\"280\" border=\"0\" /></a></p>\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 北京音乐家协会优秀歌曲进校园启动仪式</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.zgxymyw.cn/uploads/userup/1003/1R059195H7.jpg\" target=\"_blank\"><img   height=\"161\" alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.zgxymyw.cn/uploads/userup/1003/1R059195H7_lit.jpg\" width=\"280\" border=\"0\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.zgxymyw.cn/uploads/userup/1003/1R100412046.jpg\" target=\"_blank\"><img   height=\"127\" alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.zgxymyw.cn/uploads/userup/1003/1R100412046_lit.jpg\" width=\"280\" border=\"0\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.zgxymyw.cn/uploads/userup/1003/1R1040K230.jpg\" target=\"_blank\"><img   height=\"100\" alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.zgxymyw.cn/uploads/userup/1003/1R1040K230_lit.jpg\" width=\"280\" border=\"0\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.zgxymyw.cn/uploads/userup/1003/1R1013K126.jpg\" target=\"_blank\"></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.zgxymyw.cn/uploads/userup/1003/1R106111X3.jpg\" target=\"_blank\"></a> <a href=\"http://www.zgxymyw.cn/uploads